<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Nethaji Degree College</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial; background:#f4f6f8; padding:20px;">

<div style="max-width:600px; background:#fff; padding:25px; margin:auto; border-radius:8px;">

    <h2 style="text-align:center; color:#2c3e50;">
        Welcome to Nethaji Degree College 🏫
    </h2>

    <p>Dear <strong>${name}</strong>,</p>

    <p>
        We are pleased to inform you that you have been onboarded as a
        <strong>Lecturer</strong> at <strong>Nethaji Degree College</strong>.
    </p>

    <p><strong>Your Faculty Login Credentials:</strong></p>

    <div style="background:#eef2ff; padding:15px; border-radius:6px;">
        <p><b>Email:</b> ${email}</p>
        <p><b>Password:</b> ${password}</p>
    </div>

    <p>
        Access the faculty portal using the link below:
    </p>

    <p style="text-align:center;">
        <a href="https://api.nethajidcs.com/login"
           style="background:#1f7a3f; color:#fff; padding:12px 20px;
                  text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px;">
            Lecturer Login
        </a>
    </p>

    <p>
        For security purposes, please update your password after your first login.
    </p>

    <p>
        We look forward to your valuable contribution to our institution.
    </p>

    <p>
        Regards,<br/>
        <strong>Nethaji Degree College Administration</strong>
    </p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
